(2, 2, 'Mirrors', 'item_display', '', '', 'Mirrors', '<p>\r\n	<big><a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&deptid=2\">Click here to view \"Decorative Mirrors\"</a></big></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	A Friedman Brothers decorative mirror is considered the most elegant, sophisticated and beautiful mirror one could purchase. Hand-crafted by Master Artisans with the same skilled techniques used for over a hundred years. No company has more designs to choose from, some of which date back to the 1700s. Each mirror is treasured as a true, timeless work of art - an investment in elegance that only has the potential to become priceless to its owner.............more.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	</p>\r\n', 'yes', 0, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', 0),
(3, 3, 'Sconces', 'item_display', '', '', 'Sconces', '<div align=\"justify\">\r\n	<div align=\"left\">\r\n		<a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&amp;deptid=3\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"4\"><font size=\"2\">Click here to view</font> &quot;Sconces&quot;</font></a><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		Friedman Brothers has one of the finest selections of hand made wall sconces available. Friedman sconces come in a variety of finishes and have custom options that allow you the flexibility to more precisely match your design.<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		Sconces add elegance, sophistication and charm to any room serving both form and function.&nbsp; Typically mounted just above eye level, candle fixed sconces reflect light off walls and ceilings casting a diffused warm glow.&nbsp; Sconces placed on either side of a convex mirror can also provide an interesting focal point by reflecting light further into a room.<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		Sconces are often used in hallways or corridors to provide both lighting and a point of interest in a long passage. Sconce height in a passageway is generally 3/4 of the distance up the wall as measured from the floor to the ceiling, and the distance between sconces on the wall is generally equal to the distance of the sconces from the floor, often alternating sides of the passageway. Sconce size should also be scaled to ceiling height</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<center>\r\n	&nbsp;</center>\r\n', 'yes', 2, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', NULL),
(4, 4, 'Tables', 'item_display', '', '', 'Consoles', '<div align=\"justify\">\n	<a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&amp;deptid=4\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"4\"><font size=\"2\">Click&nbsp;here to view</font>&nbsp;&quot;Consoles &amp; Tables&quot;</font></a><br />\n	<br />\n	<br />\n	A console table is an architectural term for a small table fixed to a wall or designed to stand against a wall. Friedman Brothers offers an exquisite selection of console tables that are hand made by skilled artisans and then hand finished to provide beauty and durability that will last for generations.&nbsp;<br />\n	<br />\n	Select from our myriad of finishes and choice of tops which include inlaid glass, overlaid glass and &nbsp;wood.<br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;We can also supply you with a template of your top so you can source your own, if desired.</div>\n<br />\n<center>\n	&nbsp;</center>\n<center>\n	&nbsp;</center>\n', 'yes', 1, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', NULL),
(5, 5, 'Cornices', 'item_display', '', 'On', 'Cornices', '<div align=\"justify\">\n	<div align=\"left\">\n		<a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&amp;deptid=5\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"4\"><font size=\"2\">Click here to view</font> &quot;Cornices&quot;</font></a></div>\n	<br />\n	<br />\n	Manufacturers of enduring window treatments for over 100 years proudly presents today&#39;s window fashions combined with old world elegance and techniques.<br />\n	<br />\n	Each uniquely hand crafted cornice is manufactured here in the United States to your clientelles specifications.<br />\n	<br />\n	Friedman Brothers&#39; extraordinary line of styles are available to meet your every need. We can also produce that one-of-a-kind creation to satisfy your clients most discerning taste.</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;<br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<center>\n	&nbsp;</center>\n', 'yes', 3, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', NULL),
(6, 6, 'Brackets', 'item_display', '', '', 'Brackets', '<div align=\"justify\">\r\n	<a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&deptid=6\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"4\"><font size=\"2\">Click here to view</font> \"Brackets\"</font></a><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	A bracket is an independent, elegant and decorative shelf ideal for displaying pictures, candles, plants or ornaments. A Friedman Brothers decorative bracket can serve as an architectural statement or add an accent to any wall. Friedman Brothers offers a wide selection of brackets that are sure to provide that finishing touch to your interior design.<br />\r\n	</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n	</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<center>\r\n	</center>\r\n', 'no', 6, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', 0),
(7, 7, 'Window Hardware', 'item_display', '', '', 'Window Treatments', '<div align=\"justify\">\r\n	<div align=\"left\">\r\n		<a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&deptid=7\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"4\"><font size=\"2\">Click here to view</font> \"Window Treatments\"</font></a></div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Friedman Brothers offers a variety of products ideal for adding elegance and style to window treatments, including window cornices, tie-backs, cloakpins, architraves, brackets for supporting curtain rods, and more! Select from our myriad of finishes including wood finishes, and faux finishes, or tell us what you want and we will create it so you can achieve the perfect look you are after.</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	</center>\r\n', 'no', 5, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', 0),
(8, 8, 'More', 'item_display', '', '', 'More', '<div align=\"justify\">\n	<a href=\"index.php?action=viewproducts&amp;deptid=8\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"4\"><font size=\"2\">Click here to view</font> &quot;More&nbsp;Products&quot;</font></a><br />\n	<br />\n	Friedman Brothers frequently receives requests to manufacture other furniture products. Our flexibility of production and custom capabilities allow us to produce custom pieces to your own specifications, including wall decor, beds and canopies, fire surrounds, decorative shapes and much, much more!&nbsp;<br />\n	<br />\n	Put simply, you can have the best of anything ever designed, or have some of the world&#39;s most talented craftsmen apply their skills to bring to life a new design as yet unseen.<br />\n	<br />\n	Your possibilities are unlimited.</div>\n<center>\n	&nbsp;</center>\n', 'yes', 4, 'Products', 'DisplayOrder', NULL),
